OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry day,
OL,6,Fwith only limited amounts of high
OL,7,Fcloud. With lighter winds and widely
OL,8,Fsunny skies, it will be feeling warmer
OL,9,Fthan on Tuesday for most.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FCooler Thursday and Friday, and
OL,13,Flargely dry with variable cloud and
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Some overnight frost
OL,15,Fpossible, and winds strengthening
OL,16,Flater Friday. Further rain spreading
OL,17,Feast Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
